- Monaco editing where useful
- terminal execution
- task/process spawning
- extension-based coding assistants
- workspace settings and recent workspace memory

Do not replace SkyDex core flows with raw Theia widgets.
Instead, wrap Theia services behind SkyDexia-owned actions.

