6. Registration in the 0s catalog

When SkyDexia exists, add a dedicated app entry so users can launch:
- SkyDex
- SkyDexia

Do not overwrite the original SkyDex entry.
The catalog should treat SkyDexia as an upgrade build, not a rename.
The upgraded build should live under the SkyeCDE hub platform so all new IDE builds can be swapped from one place.

7. Acceptance criteria

SkyDexia is done when:
- SkyDex still exists untouched as its own product surface.
- SkyDexia launches from the 0s catalog as a full app.
- SkyDexia can browse files, edit files, spin up servers, and open the resulting built app.
- Theia powers the coding substrate, but the visible product identity remains SkyDex.
- No launch path falls back to preview widgets for SkyDexia app pages.

